{"tid":106001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump：伊朗就黎收皮果陣，美國竟然俾成萬億幫佢續命","createTime":"2017-02-03T10:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T17:41:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2c241f7d7c259b7db5a28c04dfd9b6ccf18f5d","tid":106001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7d30ecce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump</a> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/PkdIrU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FPkdIrU.jpg&h=8fc3cdf0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當年伊朗就黎收皮果陣，美國竟然幫佢續命，俾左1500億美金佢(約萬億港幣) <br />\n<br />\n因為伊朗射彈道導彈，我地已經將佢「提上日程」，多謝之前美國同佢做既交易"},{"pid":"597d0f8fb6f91bae31efa771115de668bc97e9d9","tid":106001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://web.pts.org.tw/php2/program/e42007/preey.php?id=69\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.pts.org.tw%2Fphp2%2Fprogram%2Fe42007%2Fpreey.php%3Fid%3D69&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7f56d12b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://web.pts.org.tw/php2/program/e42007/preey.php?id=69</a> <br />\nOn one's last legs 只剩一隻腳？ <br />\n<br />\n這個俚語可以用來形容人或物品。形容人的時候，代表的是奄奄一息，或者離死期不遠的意思，譬如說that old man is on his last legs，就是說那個老頭可能快蒙主寵召了。而如果用來指稱公司或物品的時候，則是瀕臨破產，瓦解或報廢的意思。譬如如果你說My car is on its last legs的話，就是說我的車子大概快要報廢，壽終正寢的意思了。有趣的是這個俚語的用法，leg經常是用複數，值得特別注意一下。"},{"pid":"6122fa23ca29fc35b75ef8e55e101c07aca1b624","tid":106001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3dc471acc21d71e91eb2cba3601a941049cb50","tid":106001,"uid":411